long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Omni Courier Pakistan lets you use your shipping account in web WhatsApp for domestic shipping. Add your account code and API Key to generate shipment numbers directly on your WhatsApp orders page.
